      "content": "i know there are people to talk to but it doesn't change the reality. the reality is that i've got nothing left. no purpose, no energy, no future. it's like i'm just running on empty and there's no way to refill it. sometimes it feels like the most logical thing would be to just let it all go. does that even make sense? to just stop fighting?",
